## About Me
I am a graduate student in data science with professional experience in banking and customer financial services. My experience in finance has provided me with insight into customer behavior, financial decision-making, and operational challenges within the industry.

I am interested in applying machine learning, analytics, and big data technologies to solve real-world business problems. My primary interests include fraud detection, predictive analytics, customer insights, and data-driven decision-making within the financial sector.

